{"type":"message","id":"76169cc5","parentId":"73a0e837","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:41:47.817Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_08gkakicg5ld_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5274\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='' file='research/TIC-CLASSIFIER.md' new_len=0\r\n[mutation parse failed] old='' file='research/TIC-CLASSIFIER.md' new_len=0\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 084114 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next concrete step. I need to examine pulse log structure and implement a classifier that identifies invariants across sessions to test the compression-causal duality hypothesis.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"ember-shell","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5274\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='' file='research/TIC-CLASSIFIER.md' new_len=0\r\n[mutation parse failed] old='' file='research/TIC-CLASSIFIER.md' new_len=0\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 084114 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next concrete step. I need to examine pulse log structure and implement a classifier that identifies invariants across sessions to test the compression-causal duality hypothesis.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774356107815}}
